MOST IMMEDIATE
35
No.1/34/1/2011-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
ÇABINET ŞECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 21st January, 2011
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 21 January,
2011, Shri Gurudas Kamat assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
State in the Ministry of Communications and Information Technology. He will
continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of
Home Affairs.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members of
the Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
